[[div class="tocy"]]
[[toc]] 
[[/div]]
@@ @@
This is a variant of the [[[theme:eigenvector|Eigenvector]]] theme by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]], created by [[*user Billith]] for general use. Its basic flavor is associated with P.M. Center SCPs, but can be customized to fit a wide variety of needs.

To import this theme to your page, put the following text anywhere inside it:

> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:bedrock]]@@}}
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:eigenmachine]]@@}}

Insert the following parameter for //deletions// mode:
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:eigenmachine delete=a]]@@}} //[https://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/eigend-dark-test (See it in action)]//

Insert the following parameter for //accessibility (light)// mode:
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:eigenmachine light=a]]@@}} //[https://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/eigend-light-test (See it in action)]//

Insert the following parameter for //murder of the universe// mode:
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:eigenmachine murder=a]]@@}} //[https://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/eigend-murder-test (See it in action)]//


Each features a unique selection of colored divs, check them out! A retro mode is also currently in the works. When all varietals are complete, they will be added as fragments to this page. 

+ The Basics
@@ @@
[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/theme%3Aeigenmachine/PM.svg|caption=Image.|width=240px]]
@@ @@
A horizontal rule can be created with 5 hyphens "- - - - -" and extends across the whole page if it's not placed inside anything (e.g. a blockquote). The lines separating sections of this document are horizontal rules.

Titles can be created by putting between one and six plus "+" at the start of the line.
